@host = http://localhost:5000

### Health — liveness probe.
GET {{host}}/api/health

### Ingest — plain text, one log line per text line.
POST {{host}}/api/logs?service=checkout
Content-Type: text/plain

2026-07-17T12:00:01Z ERROR disk full on /var/lib/data
[warn] slow response from payment gateway
user 4711 clicked the big red button

### Ingest — blank lines are skipped, not rejected.
POST {{host}}/api/logs?service=checkout
Content-Type: text/plain

FATAL replication lag 45s exceeds limit

INFO all pods green again

### Recent errors — the read side. Level >= Error, inside the last N minutes.
GET {{host}}/api/logs/recent-errors?minutes=15&take=20

### Recent errors — filtered by service (case-insensitive match).
GET {{host}}/api/logs/recent-errors?minutes=15&service=CHECKOUT
